To-Do List Glassmorphism
A simple task list app with a modern design based on the glassmorphism effect, built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Features
Add new tasks.

Edit existing tasks.

Mark tasks as completed.

Delete tasks.

Progress bar showing the percentage of completed tasks.

Motivational message when all tasks are completed.

Confetti animation upon completing all tasks.

Automatic saving using localStorage to keep tasks between sessions.

Validation to avoid adding duplicate tasks.

Responsive design with modern glassmorphism visual effect.

Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3 (Glassmorphism and animations)

JavaScript ES6+

Font Awesome for icons

tsParticles Confetti for confetti animation

How to Use
Clone or download the repository.

Open the index.html file in your preferred browser.

Type a task in the input box and click the + button to add.

Use the edit, delete, or mark as completed buttons.

Watch the progress bar update as you advance.

Enjoy the confetti animation when all tasks are completed!

